title: Vox Machina Ep. 27 - The Path to Whitestone
description: Greyskull Keep is infiltrated by ghostly attackers as Vox Machina prepares to make their way Northeast to Whitestone to confront the Briarwoods head on. Meanwhile, Keyleth begins to suspect the mysterious power that seems to hold sway over Percy...
